Player primary scenario:
    1. select tile in which direction you want to move.
    2. click move button.
    3. select tile you want to shoot at.
    4. click shoot button.
    5. click end turn
    
Secondary scenarios:
    a. after 2: Select a new tile and move again, repeat until no moves remain. Then continue with step 3.
    b. after 4. If moves still reamin, select tile and click move. Then jump to step 5.
    